						<p>On a pillar of a rock-cut cave in the hill at the place.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Kulōttuṅga-chōḷadēva I: Year 48 = 1117-18 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This unfinished record mentions the temple of Tirumalai uḍaiya-mahādēvaat Tirukkuṉṟakkuḍi, one of the villages irrigated by (the river) Tēnāṟu in Rājēndraśōḻa-vaḷanāḍu in Rājarāja-pāṇḍināḍu.</p>						

